subNode:value.scalar:string: SELECT cm.*, c.`firstname` AS cfirstname, c.`lastname` AS clastname, e.`firstname` AS efirstname, e.`lastname` AS elastname, (COUNT(cm.id_customer_message) = 0 AND ct.id_customer != 0) AS is_new_for_me FROM `
customer_thread` ct ON ct.`id_customer_thread` = cm.`id_customer_thread` LEFT JOIN `
customer` c ON ct.`id_customer` = c.`id_customer` LEFT OUTER JOIN `
employee` e ON e.`id_employee` = cm.`id_employee` WHERE ct.id_order =
GROUP BY cm.id_customer_message ORDER BY cm.date_add DESC
